    <title>Arduino UNO 连接光敏传感器</title>
    <link href="/2026/04/13/Arduino-UNO-%E8%BF%9E%E6%8E%A5%E5%85%89%E6%95%8F%E4%BC%A0%E6%84%9F%E5%99%A8/"/>
    <url>/2026/04/13/Arduino-UNO-%E8%BF%9E%E6%8E%A5%E5%85%89%E6%95%8F%E4%BC%A0%E6%84%9F%E5%99%A8/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><u>大家好！&#x3D;)  </u></p><h2 id="今天的实验是：使用Arduino-UNO-R3-连接光敏传感器"><a href="#今天的实验是：使用Arduino-UNO-R3-连接光敏传感器" class="headerlink" title="今天的实验是：使用Arduino UNO R3 连接光敏传感器"></a>今天的实验是：使用Arduino UNO R3 连接光敏传感器</h2><table><thead><tr><th align="left">实验材料</th><th>数量</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="left">Arduino UNO R3</td><td>1</td></tr><tr><td align="left">光敏传感器</td><td>1</td></tr></tbody></table><h3 id="1-原理"><a href="#1-原理" class="headerlink" title="1.原理"></a>1.原理</h3><h3 id="光敏传感器内置光敏电阻"><a href="#光敏传感器内置光敏电阻" class="headerlink" title="光敏传感器内置光敏电阻"></a>光敏传感器内置光敏电阻</h3><p>光敏电阻是一种半导体器件，其阻值会随光照强度的变化而变化：</p><ul><li><strong>光照越强</strong>，阻值<strong>越小</strong></li><li><strong>光照越弱</strong>，阻值**越大</li></ul><h3 id="2-连接硬件"><a href="#2-连接硬件" class="headerlink" title="2.连接硬件"></a>2.连接硬件</h3><table><thead><tr><th>光敏传感器</th><th>Arduino UNO</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>VCC</td><td>5V&#x2F;3.3V</td></tr><tr><td>GND</td><td>GND</td></tr><tr><td>AO</td><td>A0</td></tr></tbody></table><h3 id="3-示例代码"><a href="#3-示例代码" class="headerlink" title="3. 示例代码"></a>3. 示例代码</h3><br/><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-type">const</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span> sensorPin = A0;  <span class="hljs-comment">// 光敏传感器连接到A0</span><br><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">setup</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> </span>&#123;<br>  Serial.<span class="hljs-built_in">begin</span>(<span class="hljs-number">9600</span>);  <span class="hljs-comment">// 初始化串口通信</span><br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">loop</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> </span>&#123;<br>  <span class="hljs-type">int</span> sensorValue = <span class="hljs-built_in">analogRead</span>(sensorPin);  <span class="hljs-comment">// 读取模拟值(0-1023)</span><br>  <br>  <span class="hljs-comment">// 输出原始值</span><br>  Serial.<span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;Analog reading: &quot;</span>);<br>  Serial.<span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(sensorValue);<br>  <br>  <span class="hljs-comment">// 根据阈值定性描述光线强度</span><br>  <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (sensorValue &lt; <span class="hljs-number">10</span>) &#123;<br>    Serial.<span class="hljs-built_in">println</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot; - 完全黑暗&quot;</span>);<br>  &#125; <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (sensorValue &lt; <span class="hljs-number">200</span>) &#123;<br>    Serial.<span class="hljs-built_in">println</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot; - 较暗&quot;</span>);<br>  &#125; <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (sensorValue &lt; <span class="hljs-number">500</span>) &#123;<br>    Serial.<span class="hljs-built_in">println</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot; - 正常光线&quot;</span>);<br>  &#125; <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (sensorValue &lt; <span class="hljs-number">800</span>) &#123;<br>    Serial.<span class="hljs-built_in">println</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot; - 明亮&quot;</span>);<br>  &#125; <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> &#123;<br>    Serial.<span class="hljs-built_in">println</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot; - 非常明亮&quot;</span>);<br>  &#125;<br>  <br>  <span class="hljs-built_in">delay</span>(<span class="hljs-number">500</span>);  <span class="hljs-comment">// 每0.5秒读取一次</span><br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="代码说明："><a href="#代码说明：" class="headerlink" title="代码说明："></a>代码说明：</h3><p>analogRead() 将A0引脚上的电压（0<del>5V）转换为0</del>1023之间的整数。光线越强，光敏电阻阻值越小，A0处电压越高，读数越大。你可以根据自己环境的实际光线情况，调整代码中的阈值（10、200、500、800）。</p><h3 id="4-上传与测试"><a href="#4-上传与测试" class="headerlink" title="4.上传与测试"></a>4.上传与测试</h3><ol><li>打开Arduino IDE，复制上面的示例代码到编辑器。</li><li>在 工具 → 开发板 中选择 Arduino Uno。</li><li>在 工具 → 端口 中选择正确的COM口</li><li>点击 上传 按钮（→图标）将程序写入Arduino。</li><li>上传成功后，打开 工具 → 串口监视器，将波特率设置为 9600。</li><li>用手遮挡光敏传感器或用光源照射，观察串口监视器中数值的变化以及LED亮度的变化.</li></ol><p><em><strong>Happy Making! 🚀</strong></em> (完）</p>]]></content>
    
    
    
